  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the disease progression in CHB/NAFLD compared with
      CHB and NAFLD including liver cirrhosis, cirrhotic complications and hepatocellular carcinoma
      (HCC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
